Anyways, the echoes from choirs signifies a songs ending, because you only hear the echo when the choir stops singing.<br>
<br>
lets see if my stream of conciousness can throw out anymore insightful pieces.<br>
<br>
I arrive a rusty gate, weathered and worn by the ages, <br>
i pass my hand over it and feel its calloused surface,<br>
I realize that i have seen this gate somewhere in my past,<br>
I look back from where i came but i cant see through the fog<br>
I look down on the floor and notice my own footprints,<br>
I have been down this path before,<br>
I am walking in circles<br>
I dont know why<br>
<br>
The minute we are born we start dying,<br>
so whats the sin in trying and flying,<br>
you came to me because you heard me crying,<br>
crying... crying out your name...<br>
The minute we find love we are killed,<br>
Just when our lives have been fullfilled,<br>
Our blood is shed and spilled,<br>
Im crying... crying out your name...<br>
<br>
